overview: The sequel to "El vecino". Javier and Andrés are two young Barranquilla residents who are trying to get ahead despite their day-to-day dilemmas. While one of them concentrates on finishing his studies to become a doctor, the other chooses to become an actor, trying not to fall into the temptations of a world that will test his spirit and his loyalty.
title: Javier y Andrés: El Vecino
